data.description: Great 3 bedroom, 3 bath home with Bonus Room in a very nice Subdivision.  The Master bedroom has room for all your furniture and even a spot to sit and read or have that morning coffee (or a 4th bedroom).  It also boasts two closets, tub and shower.  Main level bedroom for guests and an upstairs bonus room ready for entertaining.  Living room makes a nice entrance with the family room around the corner.  Kitchen has lots of storage, an Island and Pantry.  Back yard has large trees for shady afternoon BBQs.  All neutral colors!  NEW carpet and finished wood flooring as of Sept first.  Take a look today!
